            "text": "My other half was diagnosed with a brain tumour a few years ago, resulting in surgery and radio/chemotherapy. She is now on various medications alongside the fear of serious seizures. KOPILOT.ID gives us piece of mind that regardless of which activity she is participating in, if anything happens someone can quickly find essential information."
