            "verified": false,
            "date": "03/03/2026",
            "text": "What a great idea/product. I know this isn't the primary function, but I found a motorcycle helmet on the side of the interstate yesterday. I pulled over and grabbed it, and it had one of these tags on it. It says, \"Tap Phone Here\", so I did. It instantly pulled up the owner's info so I reached out to him and he got his helmet back."
          }
